title: Secret War 01-05 (2004-2005|Digital-Empire)
description:
This limited series by Brian Michael Bendis looks at a black ops mission that only Nick Fury could pull off - with a little help from his super-powered friends, of course. Promotional info for the collected edition - "Starring Wolverine, Spider-Man, Daredevil, Captain America, Black Widow, Luke Cage and more! Brian Michael Bendis, the most popular and acclaimed writer in comics, reveals the darkest chapter in Marvel Universe history! When Nick Fury discovers a disturbing connection between many of Marvel's deadliest villains, he assembles a ragtag team of the MU's most misunderstood heroes for a secret mission to do what the U.S. government could never allow - eventually leading to a super-powered blowout between a who's who of NYC heroes and mutants! Featuring the American debut of the stunning, fully painted work of Italian artist Gabrielle Dell'otto."

All of the individual five issues are in digital format, thanks to Empire. Please seed, and enjoy! :-)
